  "summary": "Malicious code in svgcraft-core (npm)",
  "details": "Svgcraft-core@1.0.1 is a trojanized SVG utility library. The module exports a function getPlugin() that fetches JSON from shorturl.at/nkw3a and passes the \"model\" field of the response to eval(), enabling remote code execution from an attacker-controlled endpoint. The C2 host is shorturl.at (a URL shortener, allowing the attacker to rotate the real destination without republishing the package).",
